      • addStaff

        public java.lang.Boolean addStaff​(Staff newStaff)
        Adds a new Staff object to this StaffDatabase. The staff ID of the Staff object must have already been set and valid for this StaffDatabase before this method can be called.
        Parameters:
        newStaff - the new Staff object to be added
        Returns:
